Specialization of nweb with initial program arguments using the 'nweb.manifest'.

The 'build.sh' script builds the nweb binary which run at port 8181 and serves files out of the subdirectory 'root'.

To test the result, run

	./nweb_slash

and connect with

	wget localhost:8181


nweb needs to be called with aguments like:

	 ./nweb 8181 ./root

